## What Implementer Must Do

1. Implement `StreamHandler` for `ModbusAnalyzer` (or equivalent `on_data` and
   `on_flow_close` methods with the right signature) in `src/analyzer/modbus.rs`.
   The `on_data` must maintain per-flow `ModbusFlowState` in a `HashMap<FlowKey, ...>`
   and call `self.process_pdu(...)`.
2. Replace `todo!()` in `dispatcher.rs` `on_data` Modbus arm with the real dispatch call.
3. Replace `todo!()` in `dispatcher.rs` `on_flow_close` Modbus arm with the real dispatch.
4. Fix post-finalize collection in `main.rs`: use `modbus.findings()` (if a proper
   `findings()` method is added) instead of `modbus.all_findings.iter().cloned()`.

